<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 18:19:17 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>纽约联储分析称，特朗普第一个任期内的关税损害了美国企业</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/tariffs-under-first-trump-term-hurt-us-firms-ny-fed-analysis-says-2024-12-05/</link><description>美国联邦储备银行(Federal Reserve Bank)的最新分析显示，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)第一任期内的进口关税在公布之日就大幅降低了股票价值，并且与股价受到最严重打击的公司的未来利润、销售额和就业率下降有关。纽约工作人员总结道。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 17:37:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/tariffs-under-first-trump-term-hurt-us-firms-ny-fed-analysis-says-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>调查显示，风险重新出现在主权和公共基金的菜单上</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/risk-is-back-menu-sovereign-public-funds-survey-shows-2024-12-05/</link><description>官方货币和金融机构论坛的一项调查显示，随着通胀担忧不再是最令人担忧的问题，管理着 6.5 万亿美元的主权和公共基金正在将风险重新纳入考虑范围，并在印度大举押注。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 14:16:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/risk-is-back-menu-sovereign-public-funds-survey-shows-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟海军：中国渔船在索马里海域遭海盗控制</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/eu-naval-force-chinese-fishing-vessel-under-control-alleged-pirates-somali-2024-12-05/</link><description>欧盟反海盗海军部队周四表示，一艘中国渔船在索马里半自治邦特兰地区的水域被涉嫌海盗控制。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 13:16:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/eu-naval-force-chinese-fishing-vessel-under-control-alleged-pirates-somali-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>日本向菲律宾提供1100万美元安全援助以加强防御</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-grants-philippines-11-mln-security-aid-bolster-defences-2024-12-05/</link><description>日本和菲律宾周四签署了一项价值 16 亿日元（1065 万美元）的安全援助协议，以在南海紧张局势加剧之际提高这个东南亚国家的海上安全和监视能力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 12:06:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/japan-grants-philippines-11-mln-security-aid-bolster-defences-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>早间出价：一个月后的“特朗普交易”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-12-05/</link><description>阿曼达·库珀 (Amanda Cooper) 对美国和全球市场未来一天的展望。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 11:03:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us/global-markets-view-usa-pix-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>习近平强调要在军队中反腐败</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-stresses-need-fight-graft-military-2024-12-05/</link><description>据中央电视台周四报道，中国国家主席习近平强调，要加强军队纪律建设、反腐败斗争，并提高信息战能力。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 10:58:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/chinas-xi-stresses-need-fight-graft-military-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>美国将向越南捐赠小船以加强海上执法</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-donate-small-boats-vietnam-boost-maritime-law-enforcement-2024-12-05/</link><description>美国驻河内大使馆周四表示，美国将向越南提供1250万美元，以增强其海上执法能力并打击非法捕鱼。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 10:56:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-donate-small-boats-vietnam-boost-maritime-law-enforcement-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>全球企业可能会受到特朗普承诺的关税影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/global-companies-likely-be-affected-by-trumps-promised-tariffs-2024-12-05/</link><description>当选总统唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 于 11 月底承诺对美国三大贸易伙伴——加拿大、墨西哥和中国征收关税，详细说明了他将如何兑现可能引发贸易战的竞选承诺。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 10:31:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/global-companies-likely-be-affected-by-trumps-promised-tariffs-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国因对台军售对13家美国军工企业实施制裁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-slaps-sanctions-13-us-military-firms-over-taiwan-arms-sale-2024-12-05/</link><description>在美国安排台湾总统过境中国后，外交部表示，中国决定从周四起对 13 家美国军事公司实施制裁，以回应美国向台湾出售武器。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 08:32:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-slaps-sanctions-13-us-military-firms-over-taiwan-arms-sale-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>菲律宾就南海事件向中国提出外交抗议</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-files-diplomatic-protest-against-china-over-sth-china-sea-incident-2024-12-05/</link><description>菲律宾外交部周四表示，已就12月4日在有争议的南海黄岩岛发生的海上事件向中国提出外交抗议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 08:04:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/philippines-files-diplomatic-protest-against-china-over-sth-china-sea-incident-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>高管告诉官方媒体，对华为 Mate 70 智能手机的需求“过剩”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/demand-excessive-huaweis-mate-70-smartphones-exec-tells-state-media-2024-12-05/</link><description>华为一位高管周四对国有媒体《证券时报》表示，由于最初准备的供应不足，华为的供应链团队正在加班加点以满足其新款 Mate 70 智能手机的需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 07:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/demand-excessive-huaweis-mate-70-smartphones-exec-tells-state-media-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>葛兰素史克从智飞带状疱疹疫苗交易中获得的收益减少；就 RSV 进行合作</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/gsk-expands-deal-with-chinas-zhifei-explore-rsv-vaccine-collaboration-2024-12-05/</link><description>英国制药商周四表示，中国智飞将向葛兰素史克支付约 23 亿英镑（合 29 亿美元），以获得葛兰素史克带状疱疹疫苗在中国的独家经销权，尽管该交易已延期，但该金额低于之前达成的协议。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 07:29:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/healthcare-pharmaceuticals/gsk-expands-deal-with-chinas-zhifei-explore-rsv-vaccine-collaboration-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>瑞银表示，在美国经济增长的推动下，全球亿万富翁财富飞跃</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/global-billionaire-wealth-leaps-fueled-by-us-gains-ubs-says-2024-12-05/</link><description>瑞士银行瑞银(UBS)周四表示，由于美国超级富豪的大幅增长抵消了中国超级富豪财富的缩水，全球亿万富翁的财富在过去一年中增长了约17%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 07:06:43 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/global-billionaire-wealth-leaps-fueled-by-us-gains-ubs-says-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>台湾官员称中国试图为即将上任的特朗普政府设定“红线”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-official-says-china-trying-set-red-line-incoming-trump-government-2024-12-05/</link><description>台湾一名高级安全官员表示，中国正试图通过加强在该地区的军事活动，为即将上任的特朗普政府和美国盟友设定一条“红线”，其中包括本周末可能在台湾举行的军事演习。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 07:03:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/taiwan-official-says-china-trying-set-red-line-incoming-trump-government-2024-12-05/</guid></item><item><title>中国汽车制造商转向混合动力车以应对欧洲电动汽车关税</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-automakers-pivot-hybrids-europe-counter-ev-tariffs-2024-12-05/</link><description>欧盟为保护其汽车工业免受大量廉价中国进口产品的影响而征收的最新电动汽车关税并不适用于混合动力汽车。</description><pubDate>Thu, 05 Dec 2024 06:43:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/china-automakers-pivot-hybrids-europe-counter-ev-tariffs-2024-12-05/</guid></item></channel></rss>